      "settings": {
        "heading": "Help Us Democratize\nEnlightenment —\n<em>One Formula at a Time</em>",
        "heading_tag": "h1",
        "heading_size": "h1",
        "body": "<p><strong>Troscriptions®</strong> creates precision-dosed, physician-formulated, pharmaceutical-grade formulas for people who refuse to settle for vague wellness and empty promises.</p><p>We’re an <strong>Inc. 5000 company</strong> building the health optimization brand we wish existed: <strong>serious science, playful execution, and radical conscientiousness baked into everything we do.</strong></p>",
