        "heading_rJpJxt": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Small Inputs. Outsized Impact. How we build one-cent solutions.",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "enable_highlight": true,
            "highlight_style": "solid-color"
          }
        },
        "text_JdipJP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Troscriptions began in 2020 when Dr. Ted Achacoso, Dr. Scott Sherr, and Boomer Anderson saw a gap no one else was addressing.</p><p>On the path of health optimization, people still need <strong>fast, reliable ways to shift physiology</strong>—to think more clearly, regulate stress, sleep better, and restore energy now, not months from now.</p><p>That’s where <strong>one-cent solutions</strong> come in. A one-cent solution isn’t about cost—it’s about <strong>leverage.</strong></p><p>It’s the idea that a small, precisely designed input (i.e. buccal troche), delivered at the right time and in the right way, can create <strong>outsized biological effects.</strong></p><p>Our mission is simple (and wildly ambitious): <strong>Democratize Enlightenment.</strong></p><p>If you’re energized by the idea of doing meaningful work that actually move the needle, you’ll probably like it here.</p>",
            "text_size": "typeset",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        }
      },
